## DHT (Kademlia) Architecture

### How It Works

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    FREE-AI DHT Network                          │
│                                                                 │
│  Node A (ID: 0x1a2b...)                                         │
│       │                                                         │
│       ├─ Knows nodes at XOR distance 2^160                      │
│       ├─ Knows nodes at XOR distance 2^159                      │
│       └─ Knows nodes at XOR distance 2^158                      │
│                                                                 │
│  Node B (ID: 0x3c4d...)                                         │
│       │                                                         │
│       ├─ Knows nodes at XOR distance 2^160                      │
│       ├─ Knows nodes at XOR distance 2^159                      │
│       └─ Knows nodes at XOR distance 2^158                      │
│                                                                 │
│  When A wants to find Node X:                                   │
│  1. A queries closest known nodes to X                          │
│  2. Those nodes return closer nodes                             │
│  3. Repeat until X is found (or closest possible)               │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

