## 2. MiniLZO Integration

### 📥 Download Link

**Official MiniLZO Source:**
```
http://www.oberhumer.com/opensource/lzo/download/lzo-2.10.tar.gz
```

**Note:** MiniLZO is part of the LZO package. After extracting, you'll find:
- `minilzo/lzo1x.h` - Header file
- `minilzo/lzo1x.c` - Implementation
- `minilzo/LZOLICENSE.txt` - License (GPL v2)

### 📁 Recommended Project Placement

```
FREE-AI/
├── src/
│   ├── compression/          ← NEW directory
│   │   ├── minilzo/
│   │   │   ├── lzo1x.h
│   │   │   ├── lzo1x.c
│   │   │   └── LZOLICENSE.txt
│   │   └── Compression.cpp/hpp  ← Our wrapper (future)
│   ├── network/
│   ├── crypto/
│   └── utils/
```

**Rationale:**
- ✅ `compression/` is clear and descriptive
- ✅ Separate from `crypto/` (compression ≠ encryption)
- ✅ Easy to find and maintain
- ✅ Can add other compression algorithms later

### 🔧 CMakeLists.txt Updates (After Download)

```cmake
