| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Outgoing** | Sign compressed | ✅ Sign **original** |
| **Outgoing** | Then compress | ✅ Then compress |
| **Incoming** | Verify decompressed | ✅ Decompress **first** |
| **Incoming** | Then decompress | ✅ Then verify **original** |

