## 📋 Updated Protocol

### State Machine Flow

```
Initiator (A)                          Receiver (B)
     │                                       │
     │─── ers_register (A's pubkey) ────────▶│
     │                                       │ Store A's pubkey
     │                                       │ Status = Connecting
     │◀── ers_register_resp (B's pubkey) ────│
     │                                       │
     │ Store B's pubkey                      │
     │ Status = Connecting                   │
     │                                       │
     │─── ers_accepted (empty) ─────────────▶│
     │                                       │
     │ Status = Connected                    │ Status = Connected
     ▼                                       ▼
```

### Failure at Any Point:
```
Any ─── ers_failed (empty) ───▶ Any
                               │
                               ▼
                        Clear all peer state
                        (including pubkey)
```

