## 📋 Summary of Changes

| Aspect | Before | After |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Enum** | `eRegAckStatus` (3 values) | `eRegStep` (4 values) |
| **Handshake** | 2-way (confusing) | 3-way (clear) |
| **Initiator** | Sends REGISTER, waits for ACK | Sends `ers_register` → receives `ers_register_resp` → sends `ers_accepted` |
| **Receiver** | Sends ACK immediately | Receives `ers_register` → sends `ers_register_resp` → waits for `ers_accepted` |
| **Failure** | State unclear | `ers_failed` clears all state (allows key rotation) |
| **Public Keys** | Exchanged in first message | Exchanged in first 2 messages |

