## 📝 Then Remove `SendDHTDiscovery()` Method

Since it's now inlined, you can remove:
- `void SendDHTDiscovery();` from `PeerManager.hpp` (private section)
- `void PeerManager::SendDHTDiscovery()` implementation from `PeerManager.cpp`

